<TEXT>
   To study an issue
   Like a true sage,
   I turn at once
   To the Op-Ed page.
   The opposing letters
   Really light a fuse,
   And it's not long before
   I agree with all views.
   -- Arnold J. Zarett.
   ---
   Unnatural Phenomenon
                                                                                                       

   Our chopped-down forest
   We now call
   The North Woods Central
   Shopping Mall,
   Where if you sniff
   ('Mid traffic's din),
   We're having the scent
   Of pine piped in.
   -- Robert Gordon.
